法規內容.條文內容:
Wearing Dress Uniforms on the following occasions:
Subparagraph 1
a formal visit to the President or Head of State of our Allies;
Subparagraph 2
attending a grand ceremony or banquet of our own or foreign countries’;
Subparagraph 3
a formal visit or a repaying visit to officials and officers of our Allies;
Subparagraph 4
attending important ceremonies or other formal occasions;
Subparagraph 5
ordinary working days or outing.

Wearing Field Service Uniforms on the following occasions:
Subparagraph 1
fighting;
Subparagraph 2
manoeuvres or trainings;
Subparagraph 3
operating inside or outside the camp;
Subparagraph 4
ordinary working days or outing.
